{"tid":1481250,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係得 黑警同新移民 最驚解放軍","createTime":"2019-08-17T15:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T15:47:34.000Z","uid":191009,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4420ba4e74af9fc7400128a630efe7f0ae735fbb","tid":1481250,"uid":191009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"黑警：解放軍一黎，接管香港，仲要班死黑警做咩？共產黨出$2400都嫌你多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新移民：辛辛苦苦係支那做雞 做騾仔 做十幾年，終於儲夠錢 搞假結婚 假專才落黎香港。解放軍一到，班仆街新移民就一無所有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正既香港人 從來未驚過解放軍，亦有腦都知到解放軍係唔敢落黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再係連登開po咩 解放軍深圳練兵，練兵摺被關我撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851e020eb439fe6f6da42d45ed5ad67a031f573d","tid":1481250,"uid":114032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:42:32.000Z","msg":"見到yahoo新聞講親解放軍要出兵<br />\n啲五毛藍絲即刻唔見晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>好喇打完飛機，8.18見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6ec724658ee26afcd7ceb743a591a2e879e6d772","tid":1481250,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:44:00.000Z","msg":"818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"214680e368d55be6e6436f7798be7dd4d9c60e64","tid":1481250,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"851e020eb439fe6f6da42d45ed5ad67a031f573